item\":{\"id\":\"item_0\",\"type\":\"agent_message\",\"text\":\"Reviewing PR `#5123` from this detached worktree. I’ll pull the PR metadata and the authoritative diff via `gh pr diff`, then inspect the changed metadata/tests against the repo’s review criteria before submitting the GitHub review.\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_1\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc 'gh pr view 5123 --json number,title,body,author,labels,baseRefName,headRefName,url'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_2\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc 'gh pr diff 5123 --patch'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_3\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc 'gh pr diff 5123 --name-only'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_3\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc 'gh pr diff 5123 --name-only'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"metadata/io.netty/netty-codec-xml/4.1.79.Final/reachability-metadata.json\\nmetadata/io.netty/netty-codec-xml/index.json\\nstats/io.netty/netty-codec-xml/4.1.79.Final/stats.json\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_1\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc 'gh pr view 5123 --json number,title,body,author,labels,baseRefName,headRefName,url'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"{\\\"author\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\\\",\\\"is_bot\\\":false,\\\"login\\\":\\\"vjovanov\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Vojin Jovanovic\\\"},\\\"baseRefName\\\":\\\"master\\\",\\\"body\\\":\\\"Fixes: oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata#4834\\\\n\\\\nThis PR provides new metadata needed for the io.netty:netty-codec-xml:4.1.79.Final, addressing Nat